#217
Entrance to the Wizard's Keep~
The main entrance hall of the Wizard's Keep stretches before you. A vaulted


ceiling of pale stone arches overhead, carved with faded arcane runes that


still faintly glow. Twin rows of iron torch sconces line the walls, and a


thick carpet runner of deep violet stretches from the outer door to the inner


passages ahead. The air hums with contained magical energy.


