Entrance to the Foyer~
A formal passage connecting the rotunda antechamber to the Keep's grand foyer.


The walls are hung with portraits of past wizards, their painted eyes seeming


to follow you as you pass. The floor is polished white marble, and a faint


echo turns every footstep into a small announcement of your presence.


