#232
Foyer~
The grand foyer of the Wizard's Keep is a sweeping space of high ceilings and


pale stone. Enchanted chandeliers hang overhead, their crystals casting


prismatic light across the marble floor. Wide corridors lead in every direction,


and the murmur of voices and distant arcane activity filters through from the


passages ahead.


