#235
Foyer - NORTH SECRET CODE FOR DOOR~
A long corridor terminates at a reinforced door set with a complex runic lock.


The sigils on the door glow faintly with a cold white light, and the air


before it crackles with suppressed magical energy. Only those who speak the


correct incantation may pass beyond. The walls here are bare stone, stripped


of any decoration.


