#258
Secret Room~
A hidden chamber concealed at the end of the secret passage. The room is small


but clearly once served an important purpose: a heavy iron desk is bolted to


the floor, its surface scarred by fire, and a scorched bookcase holds nothing


but ash. Whatever knowledge was stored here was destroyed with great care. A


single sealed iron box remains untouched in the corner, its lock intact.


